title: Your Mom Got Mugged?! | Sal & Chris Present: Hey Babe! | EP 17
description:
Hey Babe! is a podcast where comedians Chris Distefano and Sal Vulcano share stories and have fun. Let your hair down & come hang out with the BABES!


This episode the Babes talk Brian Regan's new episode, bitcoin again?!? Manscaped sent Chris something weird, we don't curse get over it! Shout out Biggie!, Are sequels cursed? Shout out Coming To America 2, Rick Ross' mansion used for Coming To America 2, the babes talk about their favorite sequels, Chris is packing for LA and its overwhelming, Chris is not gonna being clothes with him, Chris hates the apple watch, Sal travels with batteries in case the remote is dead at a hotel, gross hotel stories, Sal once stormed out of a hotel, new Hey Babe game is Sal or Serial Killer?, you better rob the right house or things will go badly, Chris' mom got mugged, bodegas were a BIG part of Chris' life growing up, shout out bodega cats!, Burglary vs thief, althlesuire, do you wear pajamas to bed?, Sal is about that comfort life, Chris’s uncle melts kneecaps, the episode ends on a Sal cliffhanger of a story: who robbed his house?! Is Chris' uncle a hero or villain? Let us know in the comments!


Rate us on iTunes! Follow us on social media @HeyBabePod
